Bello Matawalle, governor of Zamfara, has distributed 260 cars to traditional rulers in the state. According to Zailani Bappa, his special adviser on media, the governor also commissioned an “ultra-modern headquarters” of the state council of Ulama. The distribution of cars and the inauguration of the project was performed by Sa’ad Abubakar, the Sultan of Sokoto, at the government house in Gusau, on Wednesday. <img class="alignnone wp-image-684557" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Matawalle-Donates-Cars10.jpeg" alt="" width="550" height="367" srcset="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Matawalle-Donates-Cars10.jpeg 920w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Matawalle-Donates-Cars10-300x200.jpeg 300w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Matawalle-Donates-Cars10-768x513.jpeg 768w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Matawalle-Donates-Cars10-24x16.jpeg 24w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Matawalle-Donates-Cars10-36x24.jpeg 36w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Matawalle-Donates-Cars10-48x32.jpeg 48w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /> According to the statement, Matawalle said the gesture was done in recognition of the status of the traditional institutions as “the custodians of our religion and culture and vehicle of cohesion and peace in our societies”. “It is in view of the high esteem with which my administration regards our traditional leaders and institutions that we decided to procure brand new cars — Cadillac 2019 model for 17 emirs, 13 senior district heads and 230 district heads across the state,” Matawalle was quoted as saying. <img class="alignnone wp-image-684568" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Matawalle-Donates-Cars1.jpeg" alt="" width="550" height="367" srcset="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Matawalle-Donates-Cars1.jpeg 920w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Matawalle-Donates-Cars1-300x200.jpeg 300w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Matawalle-Donates-Cars1-768x513.jpeg 768w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Matawalle-Donates-Cars1-24x16.jpeg 24w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Matawalle-Donates-Cars1-36x24.jpeg 36w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Matawalle-Donates-Cars1-48x32.jpeg 48w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /> “I would like to assure you that my administration will continue to work in line with the mission of uplifting the dignity and sanctity of our traditional institutions through all possible means. “We are currently rehabilitating and reconstructing some of the palaces of our emirs across the state. Some of these projects would soon be completed.” <img class="alignnone wp-image-684524" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Car-donation-by-Matawalle3.jpg" alt="" width="550" height="367" srcset="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Car-donation-by-Matawalle3.jpg 920w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Car-donation-by-Matawalle3-300x200.jpg 300w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Car-donation-by-Matawalle3-768x513.jpg 768w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Car-donation-by-Matawalle3-24x16.jpg 24w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Car-donation-by-Matawalle3-36x24.jpg 36w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Car-donation-by-Matawalle3-48x32.jpg 48w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /> Commenting on the gesture, the sultan expressed his gratitude to Matawalle for his concern for the welfare of “the two important institutions which still remain the thread that holds our society together”. <img class="alignnone wp-image-684565" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Matawalle-Donates-Cars3.jpeg" alt="" width="550" height="410" srcset="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Matawalle-Donates-Cars3.jpeg 1000w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Matawalle-Donates-Cars3-300x224.jpeg 300w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Matawalle-Donates-Cars3-768x572.jpeg 768w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Matawalle-Donates-Cars3-24x18.jpeg 24w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Matawalle-Donates-Cars3-36x27.jpeg 36w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Matawalle-Donates-Cars3-48x36.jpeg 48w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /> He urged beneficiaries of the gesture to continue to support the Zamfara government by rendering their best in ending the challenges facing the people. <img class="alignnone wp-image-684563" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Matawalle-Donates-Cars4.jpeg" alt="" width="550" height="367" srcset="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Matawalle-Donates-Cars4.jpeg 837w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Matawalle-Donates-Cars4-300x200.jpeg 300w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Matawalle-Donates-Cars4-768x513.jpeg 768w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Matawalle-Donates-Cars4-24x16.jpeg 24w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Matawalle-Donates-Cars4-36x24.jpeg 36w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Matawalle-Donates-Cars4-48x32.jpeg 48w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /> <img class="alignnone wp-image-684561" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Matawalle-Donates-Cars5.jpeg" alt="" width="550" height="367" srcset="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content